## Cross‑Cutting: Money Tracking & Deep Insights

Across all lanes, include a **Right‑side collapsible panel** with:

- Cash & Runway Snapshot
  - Pull from:
    - Stripe MRR.
    - Bank balance (manually entered or connected).
  - Show:
    - Runway at current burn.
    - “What if” slider: change spend/growth; see runway update.

- Cohort & Product Metrics
  - Core SaaS metrics: ARR/MRR, NRR, CAC, payback, LTV, activation. [gainsight](https://www.gainsight.com/essential-guide/product-management-metrics/enterprise-product-metrics/)
  - Simple views:
    - New signups vs active users vs active companies. [ofspace](https://www.ofspace.co/blog/saas-dashboard)
    - Time‑to‑first‑value and retention for each lane.

- “Insights” feed
  - Populated by agents that run nightly:
    - “Lane X has 2x better conversion than Lane Y; raise prices by 10%.”
    - “Agency cohort ABC has rising error rates on provider Z.”
    - “Runner R3 is underpaid relative to revenue generated; consider tier bump.”
  - Each insight has:
    - “Apply” button → writes changes (e.g., updates PricingRule, security_profile, or affiliate tier).

